 SetAPen grey220
  print Your inanimate objects are always hilited in
 setapen red250
  print  red,
 setapen grey220
  print  because they cannot be moved around.
  print
  print
  print Some inanimate objects can still be commanded to attack or shoot, and will have the same hilite as one of your creatures.
showpage
waitmouseorkey
